      "value": "<p>&gt;<a class=\"entity-link\" data-pack=\"sfrpg.class-features\" data-id=\"hIhgdXnqGHBm0A64\" draggable=\"true\"><i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i> Envoy Improvisation</a></p>\n        <p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl18_LabelName\">You can make an attack that throws your enemy off-balance. As a standard action, you can make a single attack against a target within 60 feet and gain the benefits of clever feint (attempting a Bluff check against the target as normal). Apply the effects of clever feint before resolving your attack. You must have the clever feint envoy improvisation to choose this improvisation.</span></p>",
